trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute" />.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> to override the behavior of a set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects.
trans-unit.target: Use la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> para invalidar el comportamiento de un conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Multiple instances of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> class can be applied to a class member, as long as each instance has a distinct <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute.Name%2A> property value; this instructs the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> to collect unknown elements under the named element into the appropriate array.
trans-unit.target: Varias instancias de la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> clase puede aplicarse a un miembro de clase, siempre y cuando cada instancia tiene un distintos <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute.Name%2A> valor de propiedad; esto indica a la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> para recopilar los elementos desconocidos bajo el elemento con nombre en la matriz correspondiente.

trans-unit.source: It is for this reason that multiple instances of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> class can be added to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: Es por esta razón que varias instancias de la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> clase puede agregarse a la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: To override a set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects:
trans-unit.target: Para reemplazar un conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos:

trans-unit.source: Create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: Crear un <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: Create the set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects, and add each object to the collection using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Crear el conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos y agregar todos los objetos a la colección utilizando la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes.Add%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: Crear un <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> property to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: Establecer el <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> propiedad a la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: Create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.
trans-unit.target: Crear un <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.

trans-unit.source: Add the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Agregar el <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> a la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> mediante el <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides.Add%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Create an instance of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.
trans-unit.target: Cree una instancia de la <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> mediante el <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.

trans-unit.source: Serialize or deserialize an object that contains the set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects.
trans-unit.target: Serializar o deserializar un objeto que contiene el conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The following example creates a new <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> and adds it to the collection of objects accessed through the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo siguiente se crea un nuevo <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> y lo agrega a la colección de objetos que se tiene acceso a través del <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> is then added to a <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> which is used to create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> , a continuación, se agrega a un <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> que se usa para crear un <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> is used to serialize or deserialize an object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> se usa para serializar o deserializar un objeto.

trans-unit.source: To see the effect of using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> property, create an XML document named UnknownElements.xml by running the `SerializeObject` method in the `Main` method.
trans-unit.target: Para ver el efecto de usar el <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> propiedad, crear un documento XML denominado UnknownElements.xml ejecutando el `SerializeObject` método en el `Main` método.

trans-unit.source: Edit the resulting document to include other (unknown) elements.
trans-unit.target: Editar el documento resultante para incluir otros elementos (desconocidos).

trans-unit.source: Comment out the `SerializeObject` call in the `Main` method, and uncomment the call to the `DeserializeObject` method, which prints out the name and value of any unknown XML element.
trans-unit.target: Convierta en comentario la `SerializeObject` llamar a en el `Main` método, y quitar el comentario de la llamada a la `DeserializeObject` método, que imprime el nombre y valor de todos los elementos XML desconocidos.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes" />.

trans-unit.target: Agrega un objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute" /> a la colección.

trans-unit.target: Índice del objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute" /> que se acaba de agregar.

trans-unit.source: The following example creates a new <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> and adds it to the collection of objects accessed through the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo siguiente se crea un nuevo <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> y lo agrega a la colección de objetos que se tiene acceso a través del <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> is then added to an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>, which is used to create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> , a continuación, se agrega a un <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>, que se usa para crear un <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> is used to serialize or deserialize an object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> se usa para serializar o deserializar un objeto.

trans-unit.source: To see the effect of using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> property, create an XML document named UnknownElements.xml by running the `SerializeObject` method in the `Main` method.
trans-unit.target: Para ver el efecto de usar el <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> propiedad, crear un documento XML denominado UnknownElements.xml ejecutando el `SerializeObject` método en el `Main` método.

trans-unit.source: Edit the resulting document to include other (unknown) elements.
trans-unit.target: Editar el documento resultante para incluir otros elementos (desconocidos).

trans-unit.source: Comment out the `SerializeObject` call in the `Main` method, and uncomment the call to the `DeserializeObject` method, which prints out the name and value of any unknown XML element.
trans-unit.target: Convierta en comentario la `SerializeObject` llamar a en el `Main` método, y quitar el comentario de la llamada a la `DeserializeObject` método, que imprime el nombre y valor de todos los elementos XML desconocidos.
